ActCanadian International Trade Tribunal Act
SubjectOrder Referring to the Canadian International trade Tribunal, for Inquiry into and Reporting on, the Matter of the Exclusion of Certain Steel Goods from the Order Imposing a Surtax on the Importation of Certain Steel Goods
PrecisOrder Referring to the CANADIAN INTERNATIONAL TRADE TRIBUNAL, for Inquiry into and Reporting on, the Matter of the Exclusion of Certain Steel Goods from the Order Imposing a Surtax on the Importation of Certain Steel Goods in order to determine whether certain products should be excluded from final safeguard measures.
